== 應用 ==
甜菊糖在[[中國|中國]]、[[日本|日本]]及[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]有較多應用<ref name = "EC">{{cite web | author = Scientific Committee on Food | publisher = The European Commission | title = Opinion On Stevioside as a Sweetener | url = https://ec.europa.eu/food/sites/food/files/safety/docs/sci-com_scf_out34_en.pdf | date = 17 June 1999 | access-date = 2018-06-25 | archive-date = 2019-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190627152208/https://ec.europa.eu/food/sites/food/files/safety/docs/sci-com_scf_out34_en.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，其中甜菊糖佔日本本土原料糖市場大概40%。部分軟性飲料廠商，如[[可口可樂|可口可樂]]也推出以甜菊糖調味的飲料。

